The paper deals with representation learning and similarity computation in a multiview setting, which is a common problem in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also deals with recommendation systems, which is a common application of machine learning in information retrieval (cs.IR) and natural language processing (cs.CL). Finally, the paper uses movies and apps as examples, which suggests that it may involve computer vision (cs.CV) as well.
